If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : jdeaton@heathcollc.com

There's no need to use remote controller or any app. You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off you home appliance, just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.

After conecting Alexa to your HZconnect products in a few steps.
1.Download our HZconnect app for Android or iOS;
2.Register one HZconnect account in our HZconnect app;
3.You need to have some HZconnect devices;
4.Configure these devices in our HZconnect app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in HZconnect skills;
5.Download Amazon Alexa app for Android or iOS;
6.Search HZconnect skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
7.Click enable skill of "HZconnect " and you'll be navigated to HZconnect login page;
8.Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;

Now all setup and finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
 "Alexa, turn on smart light", 
"Alexa ,turn off smart light", 
"Alexa, dim back patio light", 
"Alexa , brighten the smart light".

Only the doorbell notification is available via Alexa, when visitor pushes button.
